# Flyway CI/CD Assignment - Shivansh (8983634)

## Overview
This project demonstrates the use of Flyway for automated database migrations using Ansible and GitHub Actions.

## Features
- MySQL container setup via GitHub Actions
- Flyway migrations (`V1__create_table.sql`, `V2__add_column.sql`)
- CRUD Unit Tests
- CI/CD Pipeline via GitHub Actions

## Instructions to Run
1. Clone repo
2. Run `ansible-playbook ansible/up.yaml`
3. To teardown: `ansible-playbook ansible/down.yaml`

